ed="T" n="0857a05"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0857a05"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000012700"><placeName>吳郡</placeName><placeName>嘉興</placeName><placeName>法空王寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A013352">元慧</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0857a06"/><persName key="A013352">釋元慧</persName>，俗姓<name>陸</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000022218"><placeName>晉</placeName><placeName>平原</placeName></placeName>內史<persName key="A006134">機</persName>之裔孫也。<lb
ed="T" n="0857a07"/>父<persName key="A013353">丹</persName>──文林郎雲騎尉<placeName key="PL000000012522">溫州</placeName>紏曹──，<persName key="A013352">慧</persName>即仲子也。<lb
ed="T" n="0857a08"/>髫齡<ptr type="glossary" target="#g280"/>頴悟，長而溫潤，畏作枯龜<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1908"/>，思為瘦雁<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1113"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0857a09"/>以<date key="j20268122027166" notAfter-iso="+0838-02-02" notBefore-iso="+0837-02-13"><name>開成</name>二年</date>辭親，於<placeName key="PL000000012700">法空王寺</placeName>依<persName key="A013358">清進</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0857a10"/>為弟子。<date key="j20282682028642" notAfter-iso="+0842-02-17" notBefore-iso="+0841-02-08"><name>會昌</name>元年</date>，往<placeName key="PL000000002384">恒陽</placeName>納戒法，方習毘<lb
ed="T" n="0857a11"/>尼。入<anchor xml:id="beg0857sgsz1"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0857sgsz1"/><placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺</placeName>，仍觀眾瑞。<date key="j20286432028996" notAfter-iso="+0843-02-06" notBefore-iso="+0842-02-18">二年</date>，歸寧<ptr type="glossary" target="#g399"/><placeName key="PL000000012751">嘉禾</placeName>，居<lb
ed="T" n="0857a12"/><placeName key="PL000000012726">建興寺</placeName>，立志持三白法，諷誦五部曼拏羅，<lb
ed="T" n="0857a13"/>於臂上爇香炷。<date key="j20297362030089" notAfter-iso="+0846-02-03" notBefore-iso="+0845-02-15">五年</date>，例遭澄汰，權隱白衣<ptr target="#n2641"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0857a14"/><date key="j20304612031609" notAfter-iso="+0850-04-03" notBefore-iso="+0847-02-10"><name><anchor xml:id="beg0857sgsz3"/>大<anchor xml:id="end0857sgsz3"/>中</name>初</date>，還入法門。至<date key="j20326592033012" notAfter-iso="+0854-02-04" notBefore-iso="+0853-02-16">七年</date>，重建<placeName key="PL000000012700">法空王寺</placeName>。<lb
ed="T" n="0857a15"/>又然香於臂，供養<placeName key="PL000000010008">報恩山</placeName>佛牙。次往<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台<lb
ed="T" n="0857a16"/>山</placeName>，度<placeName key="PL000000014426">石橋</placeName>，利有攸往，略無憂虞焉。<date key="j20355242040147" notAfter-iso="+0873-08-18" notBefore-iso="+0860-12-21"><name>咸通</name><lb
ed="T" n="0857a17"/>中</date>，隨送佛中指骨舍利<ptr target="#n2918"/>，往<placeName key="PL000000042886"><placeName>鳳翔</placeName><placeName>重真寺</placeName></placeName>。<anchor xml:id="beg0857sgsz4"/>煉<anchor xml:id="end0857sgsz4"/><lb
ed="T" n="0857a18"/>左<anchor xml:id="beg0857001"/>拇<anchor xml:id="end0857001"/>指，口誦《法華經》，其指不踰月復生如<lb
ed="T" n="0857a19"/>故。<date key="j20483402048723" notAfter-iso="+0897-02-09" notBefore-iso="+0896-01-23"><name>乾寧</name>三年</date>，偶云乖悆。<date key="j20486332048633" when-iso="+0896-11-11">九月二十八日</date>，歸<lb
ed="T" n="0857a20"/>寂于<placeName key="PL000000059400">尊勝院</placeName><ptr target="#n2919"/>，報齡七十八，僧臘五十八。弟子<lb
ed="T" n="0857a21"/><persName key="A013360">端肅</persName>等奉神座葬之<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳</placeName><placeName key="PL000000013239">會</placeName>之間，謂為<persName key="A013352">三白<lb
ed="T" n="0857a22"/>和尚</persName>焉。其<anchor xml:id="beg0857sgsz5"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0857sgsz5"/>拜誦持，不勝其計，如別錄<lb
ed="T" n="0857a23"/>也。</p><p xml:id="pT50p0857a2401"><lb
ed="T" n="0857a24"/>系曰：<anchor xml:id="beg0857sgsz6"/>煉<anchor xml:id="end0857sgsz6"/>大拇指，火盡灰飛，如何於焦炭之<lb
ed="T" n="0857a25"/>末，骨肉隨生不久如故？此與火中蓮<anchor xml:id="beg0857sgsz7"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0857sgsz7"/><ptr target="#n2920"/>，同<lb
ed="T" n="0857a26"/>種而異態耳。何謂三白？通曰：「事理二種：一<lb
ed="T" n="0857a27"/>白飯、白水、白鹽，事也；二身不遍觸，口誦真<lb
ed="T" n="0857a28"/>經，意不妄緣。此三明白，非黑業也。故<anchor xml:id="beg0857sgsz9"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>亨</sic><corr>享</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0857sgsz9"/>此<lb
ed="T" n="0857a29"/>名歟。」</p>
